==English==
===Verb===
{{en-verb|pump up|pumps up|pumped up|pumping up}}
* To [[inflate]] by means of a [[pump]].
* To inflate with a pumping action.
* (''fig.'') To [[excite]] a person or group to a [[frenzy]].
* {{bodybuilding}}: To cause the [[muscle]]s to swell by means of focussed [[weightlifting]].